    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54B32 inline-six powerhouse. The engine features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, providing a linear power delivery and a distinctive 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis retains its communicative handling characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension. While the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and structural integrity remain robust, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
